sentences.sentence: So it began to look tackier and tackier till in the beginning of second millennium it became looking really time-worn and run-down.
sentences.translation: 于是开始寻找庸俗和庸俗的第二个千年的开始寻找，直到它成为真正的时间，破旧和运行了。

sentences.sentence: Rubber outsole consists of a softer , tackier rubber compound designed specifically to provide ample traction in the wettest and slickest weather conditions .
sentences.translation: 橡胶外底，粘性橡胶封口胶配方设计，提供特别充分的牵引力，特别适合潮湿光滑的环境使用。
